               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Sǝnkǝssar "Synaxarion" for the first half of the year (fols.
                     3ra-217vb)&#xD; I-1) Maskaram (fols. 3ra-34va) &#xD; I-2) Ṭǝqǝmt (fols.
                     35ra-65vc)&#xD; I-3) Ḫǝdār (fols. 66ra-101vc)&#xD; I-4) Tāḫśāś (fols.
                     102ra-139vb) &#xD; I-5) Ṭǝrr (fols. 140ra-189rc)&#xD; I-6) Yakkātit (fols.
                     189va l.8 – 217vb) &#xD; The commemorative notices are followed by
                     ʿarke-hymns.</summary>
