                        <seg type="rubrication">Nomina sacra; names of the donors; incipits of the
                           commemorative notices; several groups of lines in the page opening the
                           commemorative notices for each month; the word salām; elements of the
                           punctuation signs; elements of Ethiopic numerals; the word maḫbär in the
                           supplication formulas at the end of some commemoration notes; some of the
                           months names in the upper margins of the fols.; at the end of the
                           readings for the month, the beginning of the concluding formula: ተፈጸመ፡
                           …</seg>
                     </handNote>
